data.title: Karan Singh Grover was previously married to his Dill Mill Gayye co-star Jennifer Winget and Shraddha Nigam. In an interaction with Times...
data.meta_description:
39K likes, 247 comments - pinkvilla on June 23, 2024: "Karan Singh Grover was previously married to his Dill Mill Gayye co-star Jennifer Winget and Shraddha Nigam. In an interaction with Times Of India, on being asked about his divorces, he said, “There’s nothing good about a breakup or a divorce. Yeah, later, when people move on, they realize that it happened for the best. That’s a good thing. ”

In the same conversation, @iamksgofficial also praised Bipasha and shared that he knows himself today because of her. Calling the change drastic, he says, “Like from being a nocturnal being to somebody waking up at 5 a.m. and wanting to see every sunrise and every sunset.” 

#karansinghgrover #bipashabasu #jenniferwinget #shraddhanigam #bollywood #trending #news #pinkvilla".
